---
/**
 * Services & Pricing Page - Houston Web Services
 * A comprehensive page showcasing service tiers, pricing, add-ons,
 * and the project process for small businesses in West Houston.
 *
 * Sections:
 * 1. Hero Section - Value proposition and overview
 * 2. Pricing Tiers - Three distinct service packages
